Lines: この期におよんで、新鋭機のテストとはね。
まぁ、実力を認められたからこその任務だけど…。
DeepL_mtl: At this juncture, I am not surprised that they are testing the newest aircraft.
Well, it's a mission because I was recognized for my abilities....

Lines: 新鋭機も興味あるけど、もう少しジャブローにいられれば、
壮大な宇宙艦隊発進を間近で見られたのにぃ…。
DeepL_mtl: I'm interested in the new aircraft, but if I could have stayed in Jaburo a little longer, I could have seen the grand launch of the Starfleet up close....

Lines: あぁ。　俺も観たかったなぁ…。
DeepL_mtl: I wish I could have seen it too...

Lines: さぞかし凄いんでしょうねぇ…。
俺だって観たかったよぉ…。
DeepL_mtl: I wish I could have seen it too....

Lines: 今回テストする機体が使えれば、宇宙、地上共に、
今後の戦いが楽になるはずですよ。
さ、気分を変えていきましょ！
DeepL_mtl: If the aircraft we are going to test this time can be used, it will make future battles easier, both in space and on the ground.

Lines: だね。　じゃ、とりあえず模擬戦の指定地区に移動しようか。
DeepL_mtl: Well, let's move on to the designated area for the mock battle for now.
